          <div class="greeting-sub">4 pending changes — avg turnaround 1.8 days, 62% auto-approved this quarter.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="kpi-row cols-4">
        <div class="kpi">
          <div class="kpi-label">Pending</div>
          <div class="kpi-value">4</div>
          <div class="kpi-meta"><span class="kpi-delta-label">2 in UW review</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="kpi">
          <div class="kpi-label">Approved (MTD)</div>
          <div class="kpi-value">18</div>
          <div class="kpi-meta"><span class="kpi-delta up">↑ 3</span><span class="kpi-delta-label">vs last month</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="kpi">
          <div class="kpi-label">Avg turnaround</div>
          <div class="kpi-value">1.8<span class="kpi-value-suffix">d</span></div>
          <div class="kpi-meta"><span class="kpi-delta up">↓ 0.4d</span><span class="kpi-delta-label">peer avg: 2.6d</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="kpi">
          <div class="kpi-d360-flag"><span class="d360-pill">D360</span></div>
          <div class="kpi-label">Auto-approved rate</div>
          <div class="kpi-value">62<span class="kpi-value-suffix">%</span></div>
          <div class="kpi-meta"><span class="kpi-delta up">↑ 8pt</span><span class="kpi-delta-label">vs last quarter</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="d360-strip">
        <div class="d360-strip-mark"><div class="d360-strip-mark-inner"></div></div>
        <div class="d360-strip-text">
          <div class="d360-strip-eyebrow">Powered by Data 360</div>
          <div class="d360-strip-title">Smart endorsement routing uses policy history, change type, and risk scoring to auto-approve low-risk changes and fast-track UW review.</div>
